      "review_summary": "The PR adds an owner-or-Gateway-`operator.admin` guard before `/plugins install`, `/plugins enable`, and `/plugins disable` can mutate plugin state, with focused regression tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +11, Tests +118. Total +129 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current `origin/main` lets channel-authorized `/plugins` writes with absent `GatewayClientScopes` reach mutation code without an owner check, and the PR tests construct that path directly.",
